high_descs: Go towards the shelves, turn left, go straight, turn right at the table.
Take the knife next to the bottle from the table.
Turn right, go to the wall, turn left, go across the room to the counter to the right of the sink.
Cut the potato on the counter next to the bottle into slices.
Turn right, go to the fridge.
Put the knife on the lower shelf of the fridge.
Turn left, go back to the counter with the potato.
Take a slice of potato from the counter.
Turn left, go to the oven.
Put the potato in the pot on the stove top on the right.
Take the pot from the stove top.
Turn around, go straight to the fridge.
Put the pot on the lower shelf of the fridge behind the knife.
anns.task_desc: Put a pot with a slice of potato in it in a fridge.

high_descs: Walk towards the wooden shelves and take a left, walk across the room and turn left towards the white kitchen island.
Pick up the butter knife on the kitchen island.
Turn right, then turn left and walk across the room to the counter top between the sink and microwave.
Slice the potato on the counter top.
Turn around, then turn left towards the refrigerator.
Place the butter knife in a bin in the refrigerator.
Turn left and face the counter top.
Grab a slice of potato.
Turn around and then walk to the stove.
Place the potato slice in the dish on the closest right burner.
Pick up the dish with the potato slice.
Turn around and walk to the refrigerator.
Place the dish with the potato slice in the refrigerator behind the butter knife.
move forward, turn left at the shelf, and move forward until you are next to the counter, then turn and face the counter
take the knife
cross the room to the counter next to the refrigerator
slice the potato on the counter
turn to face the refrigerator, move back slightly
open the refrigerator, place the knife in the refrigerator, and close the refrigerator door
turn left and move back to the sliced potato
take a potato slice
cross the room to the oven
place the slice in the frying pan
take the frying pan
cross the room to the refrigerator
open the refrigerator door, place the pan in the refrigerator behind the knife, and close the door
anns.task_desc: place two items in the refrigerator: 1. a knife 2. a pan with a potato slice
